- title: Announcement
  image: carousel2_bg.jpg
  message: >   RBCDSAI have been working on several timely projects to model the infection spread and analyse other COVID-19 related data. In particular,  RBCDSAI partnered with Facebook Data For Good and gained access to anonymized movement data of facebook users. We also utilized open-sourced COVID-19 case database offered by covid19india.org.
  link: https://rbcdsai.iitm.ac.in/covid19/

